Opens a stream in a player using \f[B]streamlink\f[R]
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B \f[C]BROWSER\f[R]
The program channel page is opened in.
.SH FILES
.PP
Depends on external programs: \f[C]bash\f[R], \f[C]cat\f[R],
\f[C]column\f[R], \f[C]curl\f[R], \f[C]date\f[R], \f[C]jq\f[R],
\f[C]mkdir\f[R], \f[C]rm\f[R], \f[C]streamlink\f[R] and \f[C]xargs\f[R].
